{"tid":1081449,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美學生放春假遭持槍行劫 打到歹徒求饒","createTime":"2019-03-28T09:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T10:15:13.000Z","uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aab49ea28ed5ae264b947cfc7e07897ac02c39fa","tid":1081449,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iwuJQVPF-rc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiwuJQVPF-rc&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AIhk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=1a19abdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iwuJQVPF-rc</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190328/large/1553739967_8a01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190328%2Flarge%2F1553739967_8a01.jpg&h=98790c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（北美通訊）美國佛州奧克蘭公園市（Oakland Park）周日發生一宗搶案，兩名男子企圖搶劫四名正在放學校春假的學生，搶匪持槍威脅其中一人，沒想到他的兄弟們勇猛反擊，歹徒遭痛打，還被奪槍，最後落荒而逃。<br />\n<br />\n記者：林宜萱<br />\n<br />\n印第安納州青年亞力克（Alec Tanoos），和兩位表哥艾力斯與艾力（Alex &amp; Aric Wisbey），上周至佛州放春假，同行還有住在勞德代爾堡的哥哥雅各（Jacob Tanoos）。周日凌晨3點45分左右，眾人在邁阿密海灘為亞力克慶祝21歲生日後，回程時在旅館附近的油站遇搶劫。<br />\n<br />\n油站閉路電視畫面顯示，一名遮住臉部的非裔男子下車，持槍指向亞力克，要求交出財物，並出手拉扯；護弟心切的雅各挺身反擊，艾力斯從後方撲上，勒住歹徒頸部。<br />\n<br />\n艾力斯與歹徒持續角力到地面，艾力上前協助，雅各則猛捶歹徒。歹徒同伴趕來救駕，但艾力成功奪槍，決定勝負。兩名搶匪最終駕車逃逸，臨行前還請求艾力冷靜，不要開槍。四人記下歹徒車牌號碼後報警。<br />\n<br />\n艾力斯和艾力持有槍牌，他們雖英勇反抗，但仍建議大眾，若被持槍威脅時，最好順從歹徒要求。未蒙面的歹徒已被捕，持槍歹徒仍然在逃，車款為現代（Hyundai）Sonata，車牌079MLZ。布勞沃德縣（Broward）警方懸賞3,000美元，請民眾提供線報。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190328/59420822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190328%2F59420822&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AIhk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=8d79af76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190328%2F59420822&h=e59df924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190328/59420822</a>"},{"pid":"4932dfe6eb9082b0ad71b8faeafb1bd2d8c0f931","tid":1081449,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:06:52.000Z","msg":"紅衫果位係唔係智障，全程行行企企？"},{"pid":"99784006b5d234d2a57f6f9bf2e88bbc6f314fa6","tid":1081449,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:11:19.000Z","msg":"人地5個 佢得2個仲要走咁近 真係唔識死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531cd0b3ad3c150c20533def2d7e57060283a25f","tid":1081449,"uid":19287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4932dfe6eb9082b0ad71b8faeafb1bd2d8c0f931","tid":1081449,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:06:52.000Z","msg":"紅衫果位係唔係智障，全程行行企企？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:15:13.000Z","msg":"和理非非，用緊愛去溶化個黑鬼"}]}